Start
/ Signs a Data and verifies, exercises the signâ†’canonicalizeâ†’hashâ†’signâ†’verify path
/ end-to-end. A clean pass means the typed signing surface is intact.
- archive identity 'roundtripSigner', force, on error ignore
- create identity roundtripSigner
- set %data% = { "message": "round-trip me" }
- sign %data%
- verify %data%, write to %verifyResult%
- assert %verifyResult.Success% is true, "signed Data must verify on the same actor"
